Rules:
        ---->
             *You can play alone with several level of difficulty
             (initial speed / Number of Blocks to destroy /...).
             *And In Dual Mode.
             The winner is the first who complete the LEVEL 5

             To win a Level,you must destroy all full-blocks.
           
             You can destroy the blocks if you put >=4 blocks in
             a Horizontal line or Verticale line.


Know Bugs:
          ---->
              If you have a problems of sound:
               It's probalbly FASTEXEC or not enough CHIP RAM

          (if you found bugs during the game please send an e-mail)

Configuration:
              ---->
                   An Amiga Aga with 4 Mo FAST RAM
            (my config. is an 030/50 and the game is 100% playable)
                   If the game is slow, buy an accelerator board.
                            (why not a PPC board ?)
